Class DrawingModelState

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.fer.zemris.java.hw16.jvdraw.model.DrawingModelState
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DrawingModelListener

    public class DrawingModelState
extends java.lang.Object
implements DrawingModelListener
    Represents the state of the DrawingModel. Tracks if the model is modified and the path to the file the model was saved to.
    Author:
    Dorian Ivankovic
